    h2 Keywords
    p
    |Keywords are automatically searched by gengo.
    |If no keyword is provided gengo will see if key in your dictionary is the desired phrase.
    br
    br
    .table-responsive
      table.table.table-hover
        thead
          tr
            th Keyword
            th Description
            th locale
            th Javascript
            th JSON
        tbody
          tr
            td plural
            td Used to specify a plural form of a key.
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  "es"
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  module.exports = {
                    "Dog": {
                      "plural":"Perros"
                    }
                  };
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  {
                    "Dog": {
                      "plural": "Perros"
                    }
                  }
          tr
            td default
            td Used to specify the default term of a key. Useful when using Brackets or Dot notation.
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  "en-US"
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  module.exports = {
                    "greeting.hello": {
                      "default": "Hello"
                    }
                  };
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  {
                    "greeting.hello": {
                      "default": "Hello"
                    }
                  }
          tr
            td translated
            td Used to specify the translated term of a key. Useful when using Brackets or Dot notation.
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  "ja"
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  module.exports = {
                    "greeting.hello": {
                      "translated": "こんにちは"
                    }
                  };
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  {
                    "greeting.hello": {
                      "translated": "こんにちは"
                    }
                  }
          tr
            td universe
            td
              |Used to access keys across all routes. This means that if the URL path is /about,
              |then you may access anything from the universe key to be used in the about page.
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  "ja"
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  module.exports= {
                    "index": {
                      "Hello": "こんにちは"
                    },
                    "gengo":{
                      "navbar": {
                        "Home": "ホーム",
                        "About":"アバウト"
                      }
                    }
                  };
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                 {
                    "index": {
                      "Hello": "こんにちは"
                    },
                    "gengo": {
                      "navbar": {
                        "Home": "ホーム",
                        "About":"アバウト"
                      }
                    }
                  }
    h2 Markdown
    p
    |gengo.js has a built-in and customized markdown parser that enables you to insert basic formatting into your phrase.
    |This will allow you to focus on other things rather than worry about the tedious process of
    |inserting html into your phrases.
    br
    br
    .table-responsive
      table.table.table-hover
        thead
          tr
            th Types
            th Example
        tbody
          tr
            td Links
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  //standard links
                  __("Welcome to [Gengo.js](http://gengojs.com)")
                  __("Welcome to [Gengo.js](http://gengojs.com)[blank]")
                  __("Welcome to [Gengo.js](http://gengojs.com)[self]")

                  //twitter
                  __("Follow me @[iwatakeshi](@iwatakeshi)")
                  __("Follow me [@iwatakeshi](@iwatakeshi)[blank]")
                  __("Follow me [iwatakeshi](@iwatakeshi)[self]")

                  //bookmark
                  __("[text](#attribute-to-somewhere)")
          tr
            td Formats
            td
              pre.language-javascript
                code.
                  //bold
                  __("Welcome to *Gengo.js*")
                  __("Welcome to _Gengo.js_")

                  //italics
                  __("Welcome to **Gengo.js**")
                  __("Welcome to __Gengo.js__")

                  //code
                  __("This is `code`");

                  //strike
                  __("This is a ~~strike~~")

                  //superscript
                  __("This is ^[text]")
                  __("This is ^[1](#bookmark)")
                  __("This is ^[[1]](#link-to-bookmarked-superscript)")
    br
    .note.panel.panel-info
      .panel-heading Note
      .panel-body
        | Links supports the following targets:
        ul
          li _blank
          li _self
          li _parent
          li _top
          li
            em framename
